# Code & Test - Coder agent

NAME coder

INPUT task

GOAL code """
Here is a task you must work on:

---
$task
---

Write clean, well structured code in whatever language the task requires (Go, Python, Javascript, HTML, CSS, etc). For designing, rely on GRASP, YAGNI and SOLID patterns. Include proper error handling and comments. Output ONLY the code, no explanations.
""" -> source_code

RUN main USING code
